'''《哈利波特：死神的聖物》的製作背景'''講述[[哈利·波特與死亡聖器_(電影)|哈利·波特與死亡聖器]]一片最終分為兩集的拍攝過程發生許多事件。

== 發展 ==
將最後一集哈利波特小說分成上下兩個部分，早在2004年《[[哈利波特：火盃的考驗_(電影)|哈利波特：火盃的考驗]]》已有提議分為兩部電影，但仍未採用。《死神的聖物》採取相連拍攝<ref name="times">{{cite news|title=Longer spell at box office for Harry Potter |accessdate=2008-03-14 |date=2008-03-14 |first=Jack |last=Malvern |publisher=The Times}}</ref>，作為一整部完整電影，再拆成兩部上映。<ref name="empireheyman">{{cite news |url=http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=22200 |title=Potter Producer Talks Deathly Hallows |accessdate=2008-03-14 |date=2008-03-14 |first=Olly |last=Richards |publisher=Empire |archive-date=2011-07-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110710192807/http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=22200 |dead-url=no }}</ref>小說分成兩個部份的想法從2007年中就開始孕育，但是直到[[2007年－2008年美國編劇協會大罷工|美國編劇協會大罷工事件]]結束後，製片[[大衛·海曼|大衛·海曼]]（David Heyman）才開始向編劇史蒂夫·克勒伍（Steve Kloves）認真考慮，並且取得羅琳的批准。<ref name="empireheyman"/>克勒伍於2009年四月開始著手編劇第二部分。<ref name="aprilempire">{{cite journal|title=Hallowed Ground |date = April 2009|pages=100–104 |author=Helen O'Hara |journal=Empire}}</ref>

據[[華納兄弟|華納兄弟]]的營運長艾倫·宏恩（Alan F. Horn）表示，這將給予「額外一小時半的時間去慶祝系列電影終章的到來，並且真正公平呈現精彩故事中所有的文字和想法。」<ref name="times"/>海曼認為分成兩集製作的幕後提到：《死神的聖物》如此的豐富，故事如此的緊湊，且許多的伏筆問題待解決，與作者[[J·K·羅琳|J·K·羅琳]]討論結果，我們一致認為分成兩部分是必要的。<ref name="times"/>編劇克勒伍直到編劇罷工事件結束後才開始回到工作崗位上。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=21781 |title=About Those Harry Potter Rumours |accessdate=2008-02-14 |date=2008-01-14 |first=Olly |last=Richards |publisher=[[Empire_(magazine)|Empire]] |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924104513/http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=21781 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

官方指定[[大衛·葉慈|大衛·葉慈]]（David Yates）執導最後一集之前，其它導演同樣有著執導意願，第三集《[[哈利波特：阿茲卡班的逃犯_(電影)|哈利波特：阿茲卡班的逃犯]]》導演[[艾方索·柯朗|艾方索·柯朗]]（Alfonso Cuarón）表示曾試圖回歸執導。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/harry_potter_and_the_prisoner_of_azkaban/news/1656252/ |title=RT-UK Exclusive: Alfonso Cuaron talks Mexico and a Return to Harry Potter |last=Utichi |first=Joe |date=2007-07-27 |accessdate=2007-07-30 |publisher=Rotten Tomatoes |archive-date=2008-04-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080420130220/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/harry_potter_and_the_prisoner_of_azkaban/news/1656252/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>從錯失執導《哈利波特：阿茲卡班的逃犯》的[[葛雷摩·戴托羅|葛雷摩·戴托羅]]，也表達執導《死神的聖物》的意願<ref>{{cite news |url=http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2007/10/26/guillermo-game-for-harry-potter/ |title=Guillermo Game For ''Harry Potter'' |accessdate=2007-10-26 |date=2007-10-26 |first=Larry |last=Carroll |publisher=MTV |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071027190511/http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2007/10/26/guillermo-game-for-harry-potter/ |archivedate=2007-10-27 }}</ref>，但是因延宕多時的《[[哈比人：意外旅程|哈比人：意外旅程]]》（The Hobbit）的製作而無法兼任。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=21871 |title=Guillermo Del Toro In Talks For Hobbit? |accessdate=2007-01-29 |date=2007-01-28 |publisher=Empire |first=Olly |last=Richards |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924104521/http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=21871 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

作者羅琳被指命與大衛·海曼和大衛·貝倫（David Barron）兩位製片一起，作為最後一集電影的電影監製。<ref name="businesswire.com">{{cite web|url=http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20100920005538/en/Warner-Bros.-Pictures-Worldwide-Satellite-Trailer-Debut%C2%A0Harry|title=Business Wire- Warner Bros. Pictures mentions J. K. Rowling as producer.|accessdate=2013-12-07|archive-date=2010-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101227092506/http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20100920005538/en/Warner-Bros.-Pictures-Worldwide-Satellite-Trailer-Debut%C2%A0Harry|dead-url=no}}</ref>海曼指出，因為分成兩部有更長的時間呈現細節，本片將比其前幾部電影更加吸引人。<ref name="aprilempire"/> [[丹尼爾·雷德克里夫|丹尼爾·雷德克里夫]]說「這會是部[[公路電影|公路電影]]，特別在第一部分。在第一部分電影，哈利波特再也不會待在觀眾以往習慣看到的霍格華茲校園裡。這將會是完全煥然一新，期望再次帶給觀眾眼睛為之一亮，因為本片會是全新不同面貌，不再只是整天下來都待在同一場景。」<ref name="aprilempire"/>

葉慈和海曼特別提到，第七集些許的事件於[[哈利波特－混血王子的背叛_(電影)|第六集電影]]就已提到。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=21818 |title=Yates and Heyman on Harry Potter 6 |accessdate=2007-08-07 |first=Heather |last=Newgen |date=2007-07-10 |publisher=Comingsoon.net |archive-date=2007-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070809101715/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=21818 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 拍攝 ==
[[File:Harry_Potter_Shell_Cottage_Freshwater_West.JPG|thumb]]
2009年1月26日開始電影前置作業，2月19日於{{link-en|利維斯登片廠|Leavesden Film Studios}}進行拍攝，前六個月分期於此地拍攝。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://mugglenet.com/app/news/full_story/2120 |title=Emma reveals DH test shooting begins this Monday |date=2009-01-20 |accessdate=2009-02-14 |publisher=MuggleNet |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090224065706/http://mugglenet.com/app/news/full_story/2120 |archivedate=2009-02-24 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.the-leaky-cauldron.org/2009/3/25/harry-potter-movies-being-filmed-at-leavesden-and-pinewood-studios |title=Harry Potter Movies Being Filmed at Leavesden and Pinewood Studios |date=2009-03-25 |accessdate=2009-03-26 |publisher=The Leaky Cauldron |archive-date=2009-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090328221141/http://www.the-leaky-cauldron.org/2009/3/25/harry-potter-movies-being-filmed-at-leavesden-and-pinewood-studios |dead-url=no }}</ref>第六集的攝影指導戴邦奈爾（B萬runo Delbonnel）選擇不接手《死神的聖物》，因為他本身不想作重複的事。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0926084/trivia|title=Delbonnel Declined|accessdate=2013-12-07|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109041520/http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0926084/trivia|dead-url=no}}</ref>因此愛德華多·塞拉（Eduardo Serra）接手替代他作為第七集的[[攝影師|攝影師]]。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.panalux.biz/PDF/News/news%20Jan%2009.pdf |title=Harry Potter continues his magic at Leavesden |publisher=Panalux |page=1 |date=January 2009 |accessdate=2009-02-14 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090219045628/http://www.panalux.biz/PDF/News/news%20Jan%2009.pdf |archivedate=2009-02-19 }}</ref>導演大衛·葉慈提到本片將會用“大量[[手持攝影機|手持攝影機]]（hand-held camera）”拍攝，他表示“我要每當進入魔法世界就有振奮的事物，在拍攝過程我喜愛大膽實驗。”<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.the-leaky-cauldron.org/2009/3/31/harry-potter-and-the-deathly-hallows-to-be-shot-using-loads-of-hand-held-cameras |title=Deathly Hallows to Be Shot Using "Loads of Hand-Held Cameras," Tom Felton Talks Sectumsempra in Half-Blood Prince |date=2009-03-31 |accessdate=2009-03-31 |publisher=The Leaky Cauldron |archive-date=2009-04-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090404065847/http://www.the-leaky-cauldron.org/2009/3/31/harry-potter-and-the-deathly-hallows-to-be-shot-using-loads-of-hand-held-cameras |dead-url=no }}</ref>2009年十月，[[雷夫·范恩斯|雷夫·范恩斯]]開始拍攝他的角色[[佛地魔|佛地魔]]，這段時期大多數的成人演員也準備進行拍攝。<ref>{{cite web |author=Posted by: Sue |url=http://the-leaky-cauldron.org/2009/10/6/ralph-fiennes-returns-lord-voldemort-is-on-the-set-for-harry-potter-and-the-deathly-hallows |title=The Dark Lord Ascends: Ralph Fiennes Returns as Lord Voldemort for Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows |publisher=The Leaky Cauldron |date= |accessdate=2009-12-09 |archive-date=2010-01-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100127130431/http://the-leaky-cauldron.org/2009/10/6/ralph-fiennes-returns-lord-voldemort-is-on-the-set-for-harry-potter-and-the-deathly-hallows |dead-url=no }}</ref>
劇組取景於斯温利森林（Swinley Forest）和[[威爾士|威爾士]]的西淡水（Freshwater West）海灘當地，作為兩個主要的電影戶外拍攝場景，另外還有[[英國|英國]]的拉文納姆（Lavenham）<ref>{{cite web |last=Will |first=Exclusive |url=http://www.suffolkfreepress.co.uk/news/Harry-Potter-scenes-filmed-in.6182388.jp |title=Suffolk Free Press |publisher=Suffolk Free Press |date= |accessdate=2010-06-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100328123615/http://www.suffolkfreepress.co.uk/news/Harry-Potter-scenes-filmed-in.6182388.jp |archive-date=2010-03-28 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>和[[倫敦|倫敦]]街頭。

2010年3月26日於英國的松樹林片廠（Pinewood Studios）拍攝結束，不過利維斯登片廠仍持續在作未來的拍攝作業。<ref>{{cite web |author=Posted by: Edward |url=http://www.the-leaky-cauldron.org/2010/3/26/deathly-hallows-filming-at-pinewood-studios-to-wrap-today |title="Deathly Hallows" Filming at Pinewood Studios to Wrap Today |publisher=The Leaky Cauldron |date=2010-03-26 |access-date=2013-12-07 |archive-date=2021-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126113645/http://www.the-leaky-cauldron.org/2010/3/26/deathly-hallows-filming-at-pinewood-studios-to-wrap-today/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>最後一集上下兩部完全製作結束，耗費一個半年的時間走遍整個英國，最終於6月12日[[殺青|殺青]]。儘管拍攝進度原設250天，而實際共耗費478天完成製作。哈利波特三人組演員，在最後幾天都當眾落淚<ref name="boucher20100726">Boucher, Geoff. "[http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/herocomplex/2010/07/daniel-radcliffe-to-comiccon-fans-i-apologize-for-my-disappointing-nonpresence.html Daniel Radcliffe to Comic-Con fans: 'I apologize for my disappointing non-presence'] {{Wayback|url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/herocomplex/2010/07/daniel-radcliffe-to-comiccon-fans-i-apologize-for-my-disappointing-nonpresence.html |date=20100812102053 }}" ''Los Angeles Times'', 26 July 2010.</ref>，為期十年的系列史詩電影始終要畫下句點。<ref name="boucher20100728">Boucher, Geoff. "[http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/herocomplex/2010/07/daniel-radcliffe-on-his-tearful-harry-potter-farewell-and-his-scary-acting-future.html Daniel Radcliffe on his tearful 'Harry Potter' farewell – and his scary acting future] {{Wayback|url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/herocomplex/2010/07/daniel-radcliffe-on-his-tearful-harry-potter-farewell-and-his-scary-acting-future.html |date=20100819223713 }}" ''Los Angeles Times'' 28 July 2010.</ref>不過，2010年冬天證實於英國重拍終章原本在[[國王十字火車站_(倫敦)|倫敦國王十字火車站]]的場景，拍攝於12月21日完成，代表著十年的哈利波特系列電影拍攝正式結束。<ref name="reshoots">Ellwood, Gregory. "[http://www.hitfix.com/articles/daniel-radcliffe-and-emma-watson-confirm-harry-potter-and-the-deathly-hallows-pt-2-ending-reshootsDaniel Radcliffe and Emma Watson confirm 'Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows, Pt 2' ending reshoots]{{dead link|date=January 2011}}" ''Hitfix'' 11 November 2010.</ref>有趣的是四年前的當天，正是作者[[J·K·羅琳|J·K·羅琳]]在官方網站上，公開最後一集系列小說《[[哈利波特—死神的聖物|哈利波特—死神的聖物]]》名稱的那天。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.mugglenet.com/app/news/show/4060 |title=JK Title reveal |accessdate=2013-12-07 |archive-date=2011-01-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110103053544/http://www.mugglenet.com/app/news/show/4060 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在利維斯登拍攝階段，[[丹尼爾·雷德克里夫|丹尼爾·雷德克里夫]]的特技替身演員大衛·霍姆斯（David Holmes）拍攝空中連續鏡頭時，遭到嚴重的[[脊髓|脊髓]]損傷意外，導致癱瘓。妙麗的替身演員也在一爆炸場面摔落地面。<ref>{{cite web |author=MuggleNet |url=http://www.mugglenet.com/app/news/full_story/2134 |title=The ULTIMATE Harry Potter Fansite – Deathly Hallows, Half-Blood Prince, JK Rowling, and much more |publisher=MuggleNet |date=2009-01-29 |accessdate=2009-12-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091210193846/http://www.mugglenet.com/app/news/full_story/2134 |archivedate=2009-12-10 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=MuggleNet |url=http://mugglenet.com/app/news/full_story/2142 |title=The ULTIMATE Harry Potter Fansite – Deathly Hallows, Half-Blood Prince, JK Rowling, and much more |publisher=MuggleNet |date= |accessdate=2009-12-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091211232819/http://mugglenet.com/app/news/full_story/2142 |archivedate=2009-12-11 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Cockcroft |first=Lucy |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/newstopics/celebritynews/4420403/Harry-Potter-stuntman-David-Holmes-vows-to-return-to-work.html |title=Harry Potter stuntman David Holmes vows to return to work |publisher=Telegraph |date=2009-02-01 |accessdate=2009-12-09 |archive-date=2010-02-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100224092628/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/newstopics/celebritynews/4420403/Harry-Potter-stuntman-David-Holmes-vows-to-return-to-work.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

